Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:17.30,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Som doma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:18.94,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Ahoj.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:20.62,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Prepáč, Keiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:26.09,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Prosím, tu rezidencia Maebara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:26.80,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:30.07,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Áno. Kto? Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.57,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Čože? Ďalšie stretnutie klubu?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:34.18,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dôležité?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:38.12,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ide o {\i0}život{\i1}?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:41.03,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jasné, už tam idem!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:42.78,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Len vydrž, Satoko!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.09,0:09:47.79,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Vydrž, vydrž, vydrž!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.13,0:09:51.84,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Maebara Keiichi je tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:10.82,Satoko,,0,0,0,,Uhm... Môžem sa ťa niečo spýtať?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:15.65,Satoko,,0,0,0,,Načo ti bude tá golfová palica?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:20.24,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Ty snáď žartuješ!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:24.83,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Myslel som si že ide o skutočnú bitku,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:30.17,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ale bol to len baseballový zápas medzi Hinamizawskými Bojovníkmi a Okinomiyskými Obrami.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.14,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Strajk tri!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:37.62,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Končíš!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:44.79,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Členovia týmu si ma zavolali na pomoc{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:47.36,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ale ja som to nepochopil.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:13.21,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Spravil som zo seba blázna,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:16.06,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,ale dopadlo to dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:19.08,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Zdalo sa mi že ťa to celkom bavilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:23.28,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Ja som Irie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:26.03,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Pracujem na klinike.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.59,0:11:29.33,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Okrem toho som tréner nášho baseballového týmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:35.04,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Všetci ma volajú "Kouč"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:38.48,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Budem rád ak ma tak budeš volať aj ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:45.92,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Neteší ťa keď vidíš Satoko usmievať sa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:47.43,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Pravdu povediac
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:51.60,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,nepripadá mi to nijak zvláštne.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.39,0:11:57.98,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Zdá sa, že máte Satoko naozaj rád.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:01.27,Anyone,,0,0,0,,To je pravda.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:05.31,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Plánujem si ju vziať, až bude trocha staršia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:11.52,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Čo? Aj ty si o tom premýšľal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:13.50,Anyone,,0,0,0,,To by mohol byť problém.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:16.93,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Už to mám v pláne niekoľko rokov.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:18.32,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Strieľate si zo mňa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:26.57,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Satokin brat Satoshi tiež hral za Hinamizawských Bojovníkov.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:35.28,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Dúfal som že vydrží trochu dlhšie, ale odišiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:36.19,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Odišiel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:38.91,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Stalo sa mnoho...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:40.38,Anyone,,0,0,0,,... nešťastných udalostí.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:43.36,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Už tomu budú tri roky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:46.18,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Vlastne to čoskoro budú presne tri roky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:50.31,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Ich rodičia mali nehodu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:51.91,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Nehodu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:56.42,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Boli na dovolenke a zrútili sa z vyhliadkovej terasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:12:59.84,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Takže ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.29,0:13:03.15,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Takže Satoko je sirota?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:06.91,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Áno. Teraz žije z malou Rikou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:11.52,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Sú obe siroty, takže musia byť osamelé.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.86,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Ale pomáhajú si navzájom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.34,0:13:19.77,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Skutočne by som ju rád adoptoval.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:21.67,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Adoptoval?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:24.44,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Ale nie som ženatý.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:26.81,Anyone,,0,0,0,,A nemám ani skúsenosti s výchovou detí.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:29.92,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Takže to asi ostane iba sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:34.42,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Chcel by som aby sa stále smiala.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:38.56,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Ja tiež.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:45.30,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Čiste hypoteticky, keby ste si mohol adoptovať Satoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:47.74,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,čo by ste spravil?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:54.56,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Najprv by som ju naučil volať ma "Pane" a potom by som z nej vychoval svoju osobnú slúžku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:56.60,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,M-Mion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:58.36,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Vlastne nie, ty si Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:13:59.98,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Čo ty tu robíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:06.05,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Nuž, ja som manažér Hinamizawských bojovníkov.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:07.76,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Naozaj?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:10.20,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,A kde si bola počas hry?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:15.24,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Je to len taká čestná funkcia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.24,0:14:18.73,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Potrebujeme Shion aby bol náš tým krajší.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:22.63,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Ale dúfam že nás zasa budeš povzbudzovať tak ako kedysi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.33,0:14:25.92,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Rozmyslím si to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:32.24,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Počula som že ti to celkom šlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:34.89,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Snažil som sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:38.24,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Aj Satoko bola dobrá, nemyslíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:41.84,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Ona je vždy dobrá.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:43.67,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Úplný protiklad Satoshiho.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:48.84,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Jeho sestra asi pobrala všetok športový talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:52.35,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Ty si poznala jeho brata?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:55.30,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Chcela som sa ťa spýtať na to isté.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:59.12,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Nikdy som ho nestretol.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:04.69,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,On utiekol potom ako ich rodičia zomreli, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:06.02,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,"Utiekol" ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:08.64,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Kto... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.64,0:15:11.37,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Kto to povedal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:14.94,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Čo kto povedal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:17.16,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Čo je to s tebou?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.92,0:15:21.86,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.86,0:15:26.55,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ale nehovor že utiekol bez toho aby si poznal celú pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:29.43,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Prosím.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:34.56,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Zdá sa že ostatný už doumývali a čakajú len na tvoj tanier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:37.09,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Počkaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:43.74,Rena,,0,0,0,,Zamysli sa nad tým, veď je ešte Jún.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:47.28,Rena,,0,0,0,,Tento rok sa začalo leto veľmi skoro, takmer vôbec nepršalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:50.24,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Počula som že koncom týždňa má pršať.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.96,0:15:54.53,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Povedzte, Satoko mala brata,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:57.72,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,ktorý sa volal Satoshi, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:02.08,Rena,,0,0,0,,Nevraveli sme ti?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:04.56,Rena,,0,0,0,,On odišiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:06.28,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Myslel som si že utiekol z domu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:07.87,Rena,,0,0,0,,Čože?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:10.36,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,On naozaj utiekol?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:15.79,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Z ničoho vás neobviňujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:17.46,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Ja len ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:21.76,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Nejde o to že by sme to pred tebou chceli skrývať.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:23.32,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Tak prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:26.07,Rena,,0,0,0,,Jedného dňa sa proste nevrátil domov.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:28.26,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Kam išiel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:29.34,Rena,,0,0,0,,Neviem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:34.42,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,V ten deň Satoshi jednoducho neprišiel domov.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:39.08,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Hľadala ho celá dedina, pridala sa aj polícia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:42.12,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ale nenašli ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:45.23,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Preto sa začalo hovoriť že utiekol z domu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:52.67,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Satoshi si na brigáde zarobil nejaké peniaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:56.59,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Neskôr polícia zistila že ich vybral v deň svojho zmiznutia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:17:02.14,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Našiel sa aj svedok ktorý potvrdil že ho videl na stanici v Nagoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:05.46,Rena,,0,0,0,,To bola lož.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:07.27,Rena,,0,0,0,,Satoshi neutiekol z domu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:10.74,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Počkaj... Čo sa mu teda stalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:12.70,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Rena, prestaň.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:17.41,Rena,,0,0,0,,Bola to Oyashirova kliatba.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:19.40,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Kliatba?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:23.84,Rena,,0,0,0,,Predtým ako Satoshi zmizol, povedal mi
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:27.12,Rena,,0,0,0,,že má pocit ako by ho niekto pozoroval.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:29.84,Rena,,0,0,0,,Sledovalo ho to až domov,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:35.13,Rena,,0,0,0,,a pozorovalo ho to aj keď spal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:36.23,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Rena!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:40.06,Rena,,0,0,0,,Je to znamenie Oyashirovej kliatby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:47.15,Rena,,0,0,0,,Niekde hlboko v mysli Satoshi túžil opustiť Hinamizawa a ísť niekam inam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:50.19,Rena,,0,0,0,,To Oyashiro nedovolí.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:52.56,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Povedala som: dosť!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:56.08,Rena,,0,0,0,,Oyashiro je ochranca Hinamizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:18:00.01,Rena,,0,0,0,,Nedovolí nikomu opustiť dedinu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:01.74,Rena,,0,0,0,,Ja som prosila o odpustenie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:04.31,Rena,,0,0,0,,Ale Satoshi nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:07.91,Rena,,0,0,0,,Preto ho zasiahla jeho kliatba.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:10.55,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Oyashirova... kliatba?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.88,0:18:13.23,Rena,,0,0,0,,Polícia tvrdí že utiekol z domu,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:15.34,Rena,,0,0,0,,ale ja tomu neverím!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:21.56,Rena,,0,0,0,,Je to len špinavá lož vymyslená ľuďmi ktorý tej kliatbe neveria!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:25.18,Rena,,0,0,0,,Nezáleží na tom či veríš Oyashirovej kliatbe alebo nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:29.92,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Povedala som ti že máš prestať.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:35.65,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Kei-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:38.95,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Sľúbila som ti požičať nejaké časopisy, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.94,0:18:40.14,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ideš so mnou?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:41.68,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:46.05,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Aha, jasné.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:52.09,Rena,,0,0,0,,Dobre, tak ja idem domov.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:55.32,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Tak ahoj, Rena. Uvidíme sa zajtra.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:57.38,Rena,,0,0,0,,Áno, zajtra.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:05.56,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Nesmieš to brať príliž vážne.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:07.24,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Nie ja ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:09.87,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Myslím že to bola moja chyba.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:13.94,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Nesnažili sme sa to pred tebou zatajiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:18.11,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ale je to niečo o čom nehovoríme radi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:24.49,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,O Oyashirovej kliatbe si už počul.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:26.08,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Trochu ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:31.76,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Satoshiho rodičia podporovali stavbu priehrady.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.76,0:19:36.55,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Myslel som si že bola proti tomu celá dedina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:39.55,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Mali na to svoje dôvody.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:43.68,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Nie každý bol proti výstavbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:47.46,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Satoshiho rodičia viedli tých čo boli za.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:53.69,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Vláda ponúkala vysoké odstupné.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:58.32,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Mnoho ľudí súhlasili s výstavbou kvôli peniazom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:20:05.10,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Jeho rodičia ale zomreli v deň Osláv Oyashira,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:09.37,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,takže ľudia začali tvrdiť že ich zasiahla Oyashirova kliatba.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:17.47,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Takže aj Satoshiho útek pokladali za pokračovanie kliatby?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:20.14,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Niečo také.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:24.76,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Pre Satoko nie sú rodičia, zmiznutie brata
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:30.29,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,a kliatba dobré témy na rozhovor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:37.32,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Preto sa nikdy nerozprávame o jej rodine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:43.78,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,A hovoríme že Satoshi "odišiel" keď na to príde reč.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:46.47,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Rozumiem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:48.32,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Prepáč mi ten dnešok.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:51.72,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Uvidíme sa zajtra.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:21:00.16,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Nehovor už o Satoshim pred Renou, dobre?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:00.86,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:04.61,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Veď si to videl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:08.81,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Neviem prečo, ale od kedy sa vrátila späť,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:11.01,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,berie tú kliatbu naozaj vážne.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.01,0:21:14.27,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Prečo je taká?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:16.38,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Rena si myslí...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.99,0:21:20.80,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Nepovieš to nikomu, áno?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:21.69,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Neboj sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:23.44,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Rena si myslí
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.46,0:21:27.13,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,že ju tiež zasiahla kliatba.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:30.08,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Sama mi to povedala.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:31.12,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Ona tomu verí.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.69,0:21:33.34,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Je dosť zúrivá keď sa o tom hovorí.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:36.72,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Rena na to nevyzerá, ale keď sa nahnevá,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.72,0:21:39.14,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,nie je to pekný pohlaď.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:43.42,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Už o tom nebudem hovoriť.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:10.51,karaoke_org,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}To get my happiness I had done everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:10.51,karaoke_sk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Pre to aby som mohla byť šťastná som už spravila všetko,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:16.89,karaoke_org,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}but had done nothing to be blamed and accused of.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:16.89,karaoke_sk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}ale nespravila som nič za čo by si ma mohol súdiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:23.44,karaoke_org,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}The sounds of footsteps became louder every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:23.44,karaoke_sk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Zvuk krokov sa každým dňom zdal byť o kúsok bližšie,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:30.57,karaoke_org,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Then I noticed the fact there was no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:30.57,karaoke_sk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}až som si uvedomila že môj čas vypršal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.58,0:22:38.75,karaoke_org,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}I was a believer in life to be myself always,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.58,0:22:38.75,karaoke_sk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Vždy som verila že môj život patrí iba mne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:45.71,karaoke_org,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}and was asking whether I would be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:45.71,karaoke_sk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}a pýtala som sa ho, či ešte môžem žiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:52.80,karaoke_org,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Give me a reason why not to adopt in this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:52.80,karaoke_sk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Tak mi daj dôvod prečo nejsť svojou cestou,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.80,0:23:00.10,karaoke_org,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}or judge me to be guilty of so many incurable sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.80,0:23:00.10,karaoke_sk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}alebo ma súď za všetky moje hriechy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:06.99,karaoke_org,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Tell me why, or why not. Complainig way too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:06.99,karaoke_sk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Povedz prečo alebo prečo nie, lebo zatiaľ čo som plakala,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.99,0:23:15.12,karaoke_org,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}maybe I overlooked something fatal for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.99,0:23:15.12,karaoke_sk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}musela som prehliadnuť niečo strašné.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.91,0:23:19.70,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Nikto si už nepamätá kedy padla prvá slza.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.67,0:23:24.58,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Nikto už nezastaví výkriky zúfalstva.
